column5: Since it is the time to consider an oil change I was curious of the different type of oils and how it works. It is quite a long article but this fellow is very passionate to contribute his findings.  http://www.ferrarichat.com/forum/faq.php?faq=haas_articles
That's very long winded, that's for sure, an interesting read. I just do what the owner's manual tells me too. The manufacturer knows their product better than anyone.
I just wasted 10 minutes of my life
Whitespinnerbait,   you're a really fast reader, cause after 5 minutes I said to myself " All this won't help me sleep better at night so hopefully it won't keep me up either????"
